{"prompt": "Generate a website for a AI startup. The website should be elegant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Aura AI</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #0a2342;\n            --secondary-blue: #243b55;\n            --text-light: #e0e0e0;\n            --text-dark: #333333;\n            --accent-color: #3f72af;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            padding: 20px 50px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 28px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 30px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            font-weight: 500;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-blue) 0%, var(--secondary-blue) 100%);\n            height: 80vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color); /* Keep accent color for hover effect */\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            padding: 80px 50px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-blue);\n        }\n\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 40px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            opacity: 0.8;\n        }\n\n        .about {\n            padding: 80px 50px;\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            align-items: center;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n\n        .about-text {\n            max-width: 500px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .about h2 {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n        }\n\n        .about p {\n            font-size: 17px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            opacity: 0.85;\n        }\n\n        .about-image img {\n            max-width: 450px;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            border-top: 1px solid var(--secondary-blue);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            opacity: 0.7;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                padding: 15px 20px;\n            }\n            nav ul {\n                margin-top: 15px;\n                justify-content: center;\n            }\n            nav ul li {\n                margin: 0 15px;\n            }\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 38px;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 18px;\n            }\n            .features, .about {\n                padding: 50px 20px;\n            }\n            .about {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            .about-text {\n                margin-bottom: 30px;\n                text-align: center;\n            }\n            .about-image img {\n                max-width: 100%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"logo\">Aura AI</div>\n        <nav>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#features\">Features</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Intelligent Solutions, Powered by Aura AI</h1>\n        <p>We harness the power of artificial intelligence to transform your business, drive innovation, and unlock new possibilities.</p>\n        <a href=\"#features\" class=\"cta-button\">Discover Our Solutions</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"features\">\n        <h2>Our Core Capabilities</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-robot\"></i>\n                <h3>Machine Learning</h3>\n                <p>Leverage advanced algorithms for predictive analytics and intelligent automation.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                <h3>Natural Language Processing</h3>\n                <p>Enable seamless human-computer interaction with sophisticated language understanding.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                <h3>Data Analytics</h3>\n                <p>Extract actionable insights from complex datasets to inform strategic decisions.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                <h3>AI Security</h3>\n                <p>Enhance your security posture with intelligent threat detection and prevention.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"about-text\">\n            <h2>About Aura AI</h2>\n            <p>Aura AI is at the forefront of artificial intelligence innovation. We are a team of passionate researchers, engineers, and strategists dedicated to creating AI-powered solutions that are not only powerful but also ethical and accessible.</p>\n            <p>Our mission is to empower businesses with the intelligence they need to thrive in the digital age. From optimizing operations to creating new customer experiences, Aura AI is your partner in progress.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"about-image\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/450x300/0a2342/ffffff?text=Aura+AI+Innovation\" alt=\"Aura AI Innovation\">\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer id=\"contact\">\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Aura AI. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Contact us at <a href=\"mailto:info@auraai.com\">info@auraai.com</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add smooth scrolling to anchor links\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}